 AFRO-FUSION artiste, Nnaemeka Stanley Mamah aka Nedro has dropped a hint on the possibility of release a new song ahead of his forthcoming EP. Currently working on his forthcoming EP, Nedro recently released some new pictures showcasing his energetic self ahead of his EP release. Signed to Canadian based record label, Timbaze Music, Nedro has appeared on major shows and tours including the prestigious reality tv show Big Brother Naija closing ceremony in South Africa, Hero Fiesta Concert in Onitsha, Trace in the City Tour in Lagos and Benin. Nedro hit the entertainment limelight with the release of his debut single, ‘Duro Nor,’ in 2016 after which he collaborated with Patoranking on ‘Once Upon A Time’.